      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="volume-2"></i></div><h3>Voiceovers</h3><p>Text-to-speech with natural Indian accents in Hindi, English, Tamil, Bengali, and more.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="file-text"></i></div><h3>Script to Video</h3><p>Paste your script, choose an avatar, and get a complete video in minutes — not days.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="wand-2"></i></div><h3>Auto-Editing</h3><p>AI adds transitions, captions, background music, and call-to-action overlays automatically.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="subtitles"></i></div><h3>Auto Captions</h3><p>AI generates accurate captions in multiple languages — perfect for mute-viewing on social media.</p></div>
      <div class="detail-card animate-on-scroll"><div class="detail-card-icon"><i data-lucide="palette"></i></div><h3>Brand Kit</h3><p>Upload your logo, brand colours, and fonts. AI applies them consistently to every video.</p></div>
