    </div>
    <div class="faq-list">
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">How realistic are the AI avatars?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Our avatars feature natural facial expressions, lip-sync accuracy, and realistic gestures. Most viewers cannot tell they are AI-generated.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Can I create videos in Indian languages?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Yes. We support Hindi, English, Tamil, Telugu, Bengali, Marathi, Gujarati, and Kannada — with native accent voiceovers for each language.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">How long does it take to generate a video?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Most videos are generated in 5–15 minutes depending on length and complexity. A 2-minute video with one avatar typically takes under 5 minutes.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">What video formats and resolutions are supported?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>We export in MP4 format at up to 1080p. You can choose from landscape (16:9), square (1:1), or vertical (9:16) formats.</p></div>
      </div>
      <div class="faq-item animate-on-scroll">
        <button class="faq-question">Can I use my own brand colours and logo?<span class="faq-icon"><i data-lucide="plus" style="width:20px;height:20px"></i></span></button>
        <div class="faq-answer"><p>Absolutely. Our Brand Kit feature lets you upload your logo, brand colours, and fonts. AI applies them consistently to every video.</p></div>
      </div>
    </div>
